            <Record>
                <Paragraph MissionStatmentId="156" SortOrder="1">The Bureau of Safety and Environmental Enforcement promotes safety, protects the environment, and conserves resources offshore by overseeing the regulatory process and enforcing Federal rules and regulations.</Paragraph>
